rComments: He's a bit of a pushover, I think, but overall a really nice guy.  Be careful of this class though -- I took it thinking it would be an easy A and ended up getting a B.  You do end up with a better understanding of the culture thought the class.
He's an interesting guy. You get to watch several films which are pretty good during the class.  Tests are straight foward.
This class is not as easy as it sounds. He rambles like an idiot and uses expressions like, "if you will", way too much.
Tries to force liberal values on to the Class.  He is not clear about what is important for exams.
Very knowledgeable. Rambles a bit about his experiences at times, but he knows a lot.
